<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Análisis de Competidores — Sushi Seven | Mercado Sushi Puebla</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #f8f9fb;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #1a1a40 60%, #0d2137 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 48px 40px 36px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 220px; height: 220px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(243,156,18,0.07);
    }
    .header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30px; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 60px;
      background: #f8f9fb;
      clip-path: ellipse(55% 100% at 50% 100%);
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .header h1 span { color: #f39c12; }
    .header p { margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.75; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .header-meta { text-align: right; }
    .header-meta .date { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.65; }
    .powered {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .powered span { color: #f39c12; }

    /* CONTAINER */
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 24px 80px;
    }

    /* SECTION TITLE */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #f39c12;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* COMPETITOR GRID */
    .competitors-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(480px, 1fr));
      gap: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 72px;
    }

    /* COMPETITOR CARD */
    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,26,46,0.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(26,26,46,0.04);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,26,46,0.14), 0 2px 8px rgba(26,26,46,0.06);
    }

    .card-header {
      padding: 20px 24px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f5;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .card-title { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .card-address { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #888; margin-top: 4px; }

    .rating-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .rating-green { background: #d4f5e3; color: #1a8c50; }
    .rating-yellow { background: #fef3cd; color: #9a6200; }
    .rating-red { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }

    /* MAP */
    .map-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      background: #eef0f5;
    }
    .map-wrapper iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }

    /* CARD BODY */
    .card-body { padding: 20px 24px; }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 0.87rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .info-icon { font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .info-label { font-weight: 600; color: #555; margin-right: 4px; }

    /* SPECIALTY TAG */
    .specialty-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f0f4ff;
      border: 1px solid #c7d5ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #2c4399;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .specialty-tag strong { font-weight: 700; }

    /* PLATFORMS */
    .platforms { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin: 12px 0 16px; }
    .platform-badge {
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .p-uber { background: #06C167; color: white; }
    .p-rappi { background: #FF441F; color: white; }
    .p-didi { background: #FF5C00; color: white; }
    .p-propio { background: #4a4a8a; color: white; }
    .p-none { background: #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }

    /* REVIEWS */
    .reviews { margin: 14px 0; }
    .review {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .review-pos { background: #f0faf5; border-left: 3px solid #2ecc71; color: #1d5c38; }
    .review-neg { background: #fff5f5; border-left: 3px solid #e74c3c; color: #7b1e1e; }
    .review-neu { background: #f5f5f5; border-left: 3px solid #bbb; color: #555; }

    /* STRENGTHS/WEAKNESSES */
    .sw-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 14px; }
    .sw-box { border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .sw-strong { background: #f0faf5; border: 1px solid #b6f0d0; }
    .sw-strong .sw-label { color: #1a8c50; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .sw-weak { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #f5c0c0; }
    .sw-weak .sw-label { color: #c0392b; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .sw-box p { color: #444; }

    /* DIVIDER */
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #f0f0f5; margin: 16px 0; }

    /* PRICE TIER */
    .price-tier {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-left: 4px;
    }
    .tier-budget { background: #d4f5e3; color: #1a8c50; }
    .tier-mid { background: #fef3cd; color: #9a6200; }
    .tier-premium { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }

    /* OPPORTUNITIES SECTION */
    .opportunities { margin-top: 16px; }
    .opp-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .opp-subtitle { color: #666; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .opp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .opp-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #0d2137 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .opp-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -20px; right: -20px;
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(243,156,18,0.15);
    }
    .opp-num {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f39c12;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .opp-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #f39c12;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .opp-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .opp-card p { font-size: 0.83rem; opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* PRICE COMPARISON TABLE */
    .price-comparison {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,26,46,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .price-comparison h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
    }
    .price-bar-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .price-bar-name {
      width: 160px;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .price-bar-track {
      flex: 1;
      background: #f0f0f5;
      border-radius: 20px;
      height: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .price-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 10px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
    }
    .bar-budget { background: #2ecc71; }
    .bar-mid { background: #f39c12; }
    .bar-premium { background: #e74c3c; }
    .price-bar-value { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #666; font-weight: 600; width: 100px; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .footer strong { color: #f39c12; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .competitors-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sw-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .opp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .price-bar-name { width: 100px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div>
      <h1>Mercado de <span>Sushi</span><br>Puebla · Angelópolis</h1>
      <p>Análisis competitivo para <strong style="color:#fff">Sushi Seven</strong> — 5 competidores identificados</p>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div class="date">📅 Marzo 2026</div>
      <div class="powered">Powered by <span>AgentX</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <!-- PRICE COMPARISON -->
  <div class="price-comparison">
    <h3>📊 Comparativa de Rango de Precios</h3>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name">Sumo Buffet</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track">
        <div class="price-bar-fill bar-budget" style="width:17%">Buffet</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value">$209 / persona</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name">Sushi Roll</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track">
        <div class="price-bar-fill bar-mid" style="width:35%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value">$350–500</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name">Kampai Puebla</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track">
        <div class="price-bar-fill bar-mid" style="width:50%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value">$400–700</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name" style="color:#0f3460;font-weight:700">🎯 Sushi Seven</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track" style="background:#d4f5e3">
        <div class="price-bar-fill" style="width:55%;background:#0f3460">Sweet Spot</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value" style="font-weight:700;color:#0f3460">Premium accesible</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name">Ryoshi</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track">
        <div class="price-bar-fill bar-premium" style="width:72%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value">Premium</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-bar-item">
      <div class="price-bar-name">Suntory</div>
      <div class="price-bar-track">
        <div class="price-bar-fill bar-premium" style="width:100%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-bar-value">$600–1,200</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">🍣 Competidores en el Mercado</div>

  <div class="competitors-grid">

    <!-- 1. Kampai Puebla -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Kampai Puebla</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Circuito Juan Pablo II 3301, Col. Las Ánimas, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-yellow">⭐ 4.2/5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kampai+Puebla+Las+Animas+Juan+Pablo+II" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="specialty-tag"><strong>✦ Especialidad:</strong> 14 años en Puebla. Fusión japonesa, Pato Pekín, salones privados para grupos.</div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Mié 1:30PM–12AM | Jue–Sáb 1:30PM–1AM | Dom 1:30PM–9PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> $400–700 MXN por persona <span class="price-tier tier-mid">Medio-Alto</span></span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-didi">DiDi Food</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "La comida es deliciosa y el lugar es muy bello. El sushi es espectacular. Me encantó el agua de coco con lychee." — Tripadvisor</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "El servicio podría mejorar; el valet ni se acerca y los meseros no tienen actitud de servicio." — OpenTable</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Trayectoria y reconocimiento local. Las 3 plataformas delivery. Horarios nocturnos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Servicio al cliente inconsistente. Puede saturarse en fines de semana.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. Restaurante Suntory -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Restaurante Suntory</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Vía Atlixcáyotl 4931, Desarrollo Atlixcáyotl, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-yellow">⭐ 4.3/5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Suntory+Puebla+Via+Atlixcayotl+4931" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="specialty-tag"><strong>✦ Especialidad:</strong> Alta cocina japonesa clásica. +40 años de prestigio. Teppanyaki en mesa, jardines, música en vivo.</div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Jue 1PM–11PM | Vie–Sáb 1PM–11:30PM | Dom 1PM–9PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> $600–1,200 MXN por persona <span class="price-tier tier-premium">Premium</span></span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-propio">Servicio propio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Si te gusta lo japonés, Suntory es altamente recomendable por su excelente oferta y la profesionalidad del servicio." — Tripadvisor</div>
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Todo muy bien, buen sabor de alimentos. Las instalaciones en muy buen estado." — OpenTable</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Máximo prestigio en Puebla. Ambiente distinguido. Menú diferenciado con teppanyaki.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Precio elevado, limita acceso masivo. Presencia digital débil vs competidores jóvenes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. Ryoshi Puebla -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Ryoshi Puebla <span style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#f39c12;font-weight:600">★ NUEVO 2026</span></div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Osa Mayor 5149, Angelópolis, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-green">⭐ 4.9/5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ryoshi+Puebla+Osa+Mayor+5149+Angelopolis" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="specialty-tag"><strong>✦ Especialidad:</strong> Alta cocina japonesa de lujo. Marca presente en Monterrey, CDMX y Cancún. Restaurante-bar.</div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Recientemente abierto (2026) — confirmar en sucursal</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> Premium (sin precio publicado) <span class="price-tier tier-premium">Premium</span></span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Rollo Ryoshi imperdible y súper atención desde los primeros días de apertura." — Tripadvisor</div>
          <div class="review review-neu">⚪ "Calificación promedio de 4.9 estrellas según comensales de OpenTable (feb 2026)."</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Rating altísimo (4.9), novedad con buzz mediático, posicionamiento premium exitoso en otras ciudades.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Recién abierto, pocas reseñas reales, precio muy elevado, operación delivery en consolidación.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Sushi Roll Angelópolis -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Sushi Roll Angelópolis</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Blvd. del Niño Poblano 7510, CC Angelópolis, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-red">⭐ 3.7 Rappi</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sushi+Roll+Angelopolis+Puebla+CC+Angelopolis" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="specialty-tag"><strong>✦ Especialidad:</strong> Cadena nacional (50+ sucursales). Menú amplio: rollos, sashimi, tempura, teppanyaki, ramen.</div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Horarios de plaza aprox. Lun–Dom 11AM–9PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> $350–500 MXN por persona <span class="price-tier tier-mid">Medio</span></span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Rollo es la combinación perfecta entre sabor y experiencia." — sushiroll.com.mx</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "Rating de 3.7 sobre 5 en Rappi — uno de los más bajos entre restaurantes de sushi en Puebla." — Rappi</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Marca reconocida, amplia variedad, precio accesible-medio, delivery activo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
